{
  "video_id": "m6X1i8khmt8",
  "title": "What a world without prisons could look like | Deanna Van Buren",
  "es": 0,
  "json": [
    {
      "index": 1,
      "start_time": 12825.0,
      "end_time": 17634.0,
      "text": "A lot of people call me a \"justice architect.\""
    },
    {
      "index": 2,
      "start_time": 18865.0,
      "end_time": 20802.0,
      "text": "But I don&#39;t design prisons."
    },
    {
      "index": 3,
      "start_time": 21786.0,
      "end_time": 23461.0,
      "text": "I don&#39;t design jails."
    },
    {
      "index": 4,
      "start_time": 23960.0,
      "end_time": 28580.0,
      "text": "I don&#39;t design detention centers, and I don&#39;t even design courthouses."
    },
    {
      "index": 5,
      "start_time": 28872.0,
      "end_time": 32799.0,
      "text": "All the same, I get a call every week,"
    },
    {
      "index": 6,
      "start_time": 32823.0,
      "end_time": 37172.0,
      "text": "saying, \"OK, but you design better prisons, right?"
    },
    {
      "index": 7,
      "start_time": 37196.0,
      "end_time": 40116.0,
      "text": "You know, like those pretty ones they&#39;re building in Europe.\""
    },
    {
      "index": 8,
      "start_time": 40450.0,
      "end_time": 42188.0,
      "text": "And I always pause."
    },
    {
      "index": 9,
      "start_time": 43466.0,
      "end_time": 44864.0,
      "text": "And I invite them,"
    },
    {
      "index": 10,
      "start_time": 45586.0,
      "end_time": 47161.0,
      "text": "and I invite you today,"
    },
    {
      "index": 11,
      "start_time": 47617.0,
      "end_time": 49949.0,
      "text": "to imagine a world without prisons."
    },
    {
      "index": 12,
      "start_time": 51101.0,
      "end_time": 54402.0,
      "text": "What does that justice feel and look like?"
    },
    {
      "index": 13,
      "start_time": 55751.0,
      "end_time": 58860.0,
      "text": "What do we need to build to get there?"
    },
    {
      "index": 14,
      "start_time": 59673.0,
      "end_time": 63395.0,
      "text": "I&#39;d like to show you some ideas today of things that we&#39;re building."
    },
    {
      "index": 15,
      "start_time": 63419.0,
      "end_time": 66371.0,
      "text": "And I&#39;m going to start with an early prototype."
    },
    {
      "index": 16,
      "start_time": 66395.0,
      "end_time": 68553.0,
      "text": "This I built when I was five."
    },
    {
      "index": 17,
      "start_time": 68577.0,
      "end_time": 70390.0,
      "text": "I call it \"the healing hut.\""
    },
    {
      "index": 18,
      "start_time": 71212.0,
      "end_time": 74319.0,
      "text": "And I built it after I got sent home from school"
    },
    {
      "index": 19,
      "start_time": 74343.0,
      "end_time": 78130.0,
      "text": "for punching this kid in the face because he called me the N-word."
    },
    {
      "index": 20,
      "start_time": 78370.0,
      "end_time": 79304.0,
      "text": "OK, he deserved it."
    },
    {
      "index": 21,
      "start_time": 80427.0,
      "end_time": 82267.0,
      "text": "It happened a lot, though,"
    },
    {
      "index": 22,
      "start_time": 82291.0,
      "end_time": 87107.0,
      "text": "because my family had desegregated a white community in rural Virginia."
    },
    {
      "index": 23,
      "start_time": 88930.0,
      "end_time": 90433.0,
      "text": "And I was really scared."
    },
    {
      "index": 24,
      "start_time": 90893.0,
      "end_time": 92690.0,
      "text": "I was afraid."
    },
    {
      "index": 25,
      "start_time": 92498.0,
      "end_time": 93648.0,
      "text": "I was angry."
    },
    {
      "index": 26,
      "start_time": 94325.0,
      "end_time": 97744.0,
      "text": "And so I would run into the forest, and I would build these little huts."
    },
    {
      "index": 27,
      "start_time": 97768.0,
      "end_time": 102940.0,
      "text": "They were made out of twigs and leaves and blankets I had taken from my mom."
    },
    {
      "index": 28,
      "start_time": 102776.0,
      "end_time": 106940.0,
      "text": "And as the light would stream into my refuge,"
    },
    {
      "index": 29,
      "start_time": 107284.0,
      "end_time": 108750.0,
      "text": "I would feel at peace."
    },
    {
      "index": 30,
      "start_time": 111600.0,
      "end_time": 113504.0,
      "text": "Despite my efforts to comfort myself,"
    },
    {
      "index": 31,
      "start_time": 113528.0,
      "end_time": 116617.0,
      "text": "I still left my community as soon as I could,"
    },
    {
      "index": 32,
      "start_time": 116641.0,
      "end_time": 118664.0,
      "text": "and I went to architecture school"
    },
    {
      "index": 33,
      "start_time": 118688.0,
      "end_time": 122358.0,
      "text": "and then into a professional career designing shopping centers,"
    },
    {
      "index": 34,
      "start_time": 122382.0,
      "end_time": 123783.0,
      "text": "homes for the wealthy"
    },
    {
      "index": 35,
      "start_time": 123807.0,
      "end_time": 125339.0,
      "text": "and office buildings,"
    },
    {
      "index": 36,
      "start_time": 126454.0,
      "end_time": 129656.0,
      "text": "until I stepped into a prison for the first time."
    },
    {
      "index": 37,
      "start_time": 130193.00000000001,
      "end_time": 134241.0,
      "text": "It was the Chester State Correctional Institution in Pennsylvania."
    },
    {
      "index": 38,
      "start_time": 134265.0,
      "end_time": 136331.0,
      "text": "And my friend, she invited me there"
    },
    {
      "index": 39,
      "start_time": 136355.0,
      "end_time": 138513.0,
      "text": "to work with some of her incarcerated students"
    },
    {
      "index": 40,
      "start_time": 138538.0,
      "end_time": 141937.0,
      "text": "and teach them about the positive power of design."
    },
    {
      "index": 41,
      "start_time": 142704.0,
      "end_time": 144772.0,
      "text": "The irony is so obvious, right?"
    },
    {
      "index": 42,
      "start_time": 144796.0,
      "end_time": 148251.0,
      "text": "As I approached this concrete building, these tiny little windows,"
    },
    {
      "index": 43,
      "start_time": 148276.0,
      "end_time": 151759.0,
      "text": "barbed wire, high walls, observation towers,"
    },
    {
      "index": 44,
      "start_time": 152149.0,
      "end_time": 156210.0,
      "text": "and on the inside, these cold, hard spaces,"
    },
    {
      "index": 45,
      "start_time": 156450.0,
      "end_time": 158299.0,
      "text": "little light or air,"
    },
    {
      "index": 46,
      "start_time": 158324.0,
      "end_time": 161180.0,
      "text": "the guards are screaming, the doors are clanking,"
    },
    {
      "index": 47,
      "start_time": 161204.0,
      "end_time": 166461.0,
      "text": "there&#39;s a wall of cells filled with so many black and brown bodies."
    },
    {
      "index": 48,
      "start_time": 167257.0,
      "end_time": 170114.0,
      "text": "And I realized that what I was seeing"
    },
    {
      "index": 49,
      "start_time": 170138.0,
      "end_time": 174875.0,
      "text": "was the end result of our racist policies that had caused mass incarceration."
    },
    {
      "index": 50,
      "start_time": 175641.0,
      "end_time": 178315.0,
      "text": "But as an architect, what I was seeing"
    },
    {
      "index": 51,
      "start_time": 178339.0,
      "end_time": 182172.0,
      "text": "was how a prison is the worst building type we could have created"
    },
    {
      "index": 52,
      "start_time": 182196.0,
      "end_time": 184744.0,
      "text": "to address the harm that we&#39;re doing to one another."
    },
    {
      "index": 53,
      "start_time": 186850.0,
      "end_time": 188718.0,
      "text": "I thought, \"Well, could I design an alternative to this,"
    },
    {
      "index": 54,
      "start_time": 188742.0,
      "end_time": 190743.0,
      "text": "other than building a prettier prison?\""
    },
    {
      "index": 55,
      "start_time": 190767.0,
      "end_time": 193463.0,
      "text": "It didn&#39;t feel good to me; it still doesn&#39;t feel good."
    },
    {
      "index": 56,
      "start_time": 194395.0,
      "end_time": 196958.0,
      "text": "But back then, I just didn&#39;t know what to do."
    },
    {
      "index": 57,
      "start_time": 197315.0,
      "end_time": 199107.0,
      "text": "What do we build instead of this?"
    },
    {
      "index": 58,
      "start_time": 200348.0,
      "end_time": 203281.0,
      "text": "And then I heard about restorative justice."
    },
    {
      "index": 59,
      "start_time": 203840.0,
      "end_time": 205966.0,
      "text": "I felt at peace again,"
    },
    {
      "index": 60,
      "start_time": 206632.0,
      "end_time": 209458.0,
      "text": "because here was an alternative system"
    },
    {
      "index": 61,
      "start_time": 209482.0,
      "end_time": 214163.0,
      "text": "that says when a crime is committed, it is a breach of relationship,"
    },
    {
      "index": 62,
      "start_time": 214680.0,
      "end_time": 217610.0,
      "text": "that the needs of those who have been harmed"
    },
    {
      "index": 63,
      "start_time": 217850.0,
      "end_time": 218965.0,
      "text": "must be addressed first;"
    },
    {
      "index": 64,
      "start_time": 219657.0,
      "end_time": 222244.0,
      "text": "that those who have committed the offense"
    },
    {
      "index": 65,
      "start_time": 222268.0,
      "end_time": 224624.0,
      "text": "have an obligation to make amends."
    },
    {
      "index": 66,
      "start_time": 225850.0,
      "end_time": 227488.0,
      "text": "And what they are are really intense dialogues,"
    },
    {
      "index": 67,
      "start_time": 227512.0,
      "end_time": 232739.0,
      "text": "where all stakeholders come together to find a way to repair the breach."
    },
    {
      "index": 68,
      "start_time": 233695.0,
      "end_time": 237520.0,
      "text": "Early data shows that restorative justice builds empathy;"
    },
    {
      "index": 69,
      "start_time": 237560.0,
      "end_time": 241540.0,
      "text": "that it reduces violent reoffending by up to 75 percent;"
    },
    {
      "index": 70,
      "start_time": 242200.0,
      "end_time": 246500.0,
      "text": "that it eases PTSD in survivors of the most severe violence."
    },
    {
      "index": 71,
      "start_time": 246877.0,
      "end_time": 248806.0,
      "text": "And because of these reasons,"
    },
    {
      "index": 72,
      "start_time": 248830.0,
      "end_time": 251656.0,
      "text": "we see prosecutors and judges and district attorneys"
    },
    {
      "index": 73,
      "start_time": 251680.0,
      "end_time": 255252.0,
      "text": "starting to divert cases out of court and into restorative justice"
    },
    {
      "index": 74,
      "start_time": 255276.0,
      "end_time": 258656.0,
      "text": "so that some people never touch the system altogether."
    },
    {
      "index": 75,
      "start_time": 259141.00000000003,
      "end_time": 262713.0,
      "text": "And so I thought, \"Well, damn -- why aren&#39;t we designing for this system?\""
    },
    {
      "index": 76,
      "start_time": 262737.0,
      "end_time": 263999.0,
      "text": "(Applause)"
    },
    {
      "index": 77,
      "start_time": 264230.0,
      "end_time": 266522.0,
      "text": "Instead of building prisons,"
    },
    {
      "index": 78,
      "start_time": 266546.0,
      "end_time": 269994.0,
      "text": "we should be building spaces to amplify restorative justice."
    },
    {
      "index": 79,
      "start_time": 270870.0,
      "end_time": 273148.0,
      "text": "And so I started in schools,"
    },
    {
      "index": 80,
      "start_time": 273791.0,
      "end_time": 277290.0,
      "text": "because suspensions and expulsions"
    },
    {
      "index": 81,
      "start_time": 277530.0,
      "end_time": 280340.0,
      "text": "have been fueling the pathway to prison for decades."
    },
    {
      "index": 82,
      "start_time": 280953.0,
      "end_time": 283840.0,
      "text": "And many school districts -- probably some of your own --"
    },
    {
      "index": 83,
      "start_time": 283864.0,
      "end_time": 286869.0,
      "text": "are turning to restorative justice as an alternative."
    },
    {
      "index": 84,
      "start_time": 288125.0,
      "end_time": 291601.0,
      "text": "So, my first project -- I just turned this dirty little storage room"
    },
    {
      "index": 85,
      "start_time": 291625.0,
      "end_time": 295379.0,
      "text": "into a peacemaking room for a program in a high school"
    },
    {
      "index": 86,
      "start_time": 295403.0,
      "end_time": 297203.0,
      "text": "in my hometown of Oakland."
    },
    {
      "index": 87,
      "start_time": 297860.0,
      "end_time": 301580.0,
      "text": "And after we were done, the director said"
    },
    {
      "index": 88,
      "start_time": 301820.0,
      "end_time": 303670.0,
      "text": "that the circles she was holding in this space"
    },
    {
      "index": 89,
      "start_time": 303694.0,
      "end_time": 306693.0,
      "text": "were more powerful in bringing the community together"
    },
    {
      "index": 90,
      "start_time": 306717.0,
      "end_time": 310288.0,
      "text": "after fighting at school and gun violence in the community,"
    },
    {
      "index": 91,
      "start_time": 310673.0,
      "end_time": 313736.0,
      "text": "and that students and teachers started to come here"
    },
    {
      "index": 92,
      "start_time": 313760.0,
      "end_time": 316426.0,
      "text": "just because they saw it as a space of refuge."
    },
    {
      "index": 93,
      "start_time": 317434.0,
      "end_time": 322845.0,
      "text": "So what was happening is that the space was amplifying the effects of the process."
    },
    {
      "index": 94,
      "start_time": 324290.0,
      "end_time": 328692.0,
      "text": "OK, then I did something that architects always do, y&#39;all."
    },
    {
      "index": 95,
      "start_time": 329323.0,
      "end_time": 332871.0,
      "text": "I was like, I&#39;m going to build something massive now, right?"
    },
    {
      "index": 96,
      "start_time": 332895.0,
      "end_time": 337679.0,
      "text": "I&#39;m going to build the world&#39;s first restorative justice center all by myself."
    },
    {
      "index": 97,
      "start_time": 338173.0,
      "end_time": 341188.0,
      "text": "And it&#39;s going to be a beautiful figure on the skyline,"
    },
    {
      "index": 98,
      "start_time": 341212.0,
      "end_time": 343370.0,
      "text": "like a beacon in the night."
    },
    {
      "index": 99,
      "start_time": 343610.0,
      "end_time": 346933.0,
      "text": "Thousands of people will come here instead of going to court."
    },
    {
      "index": 100,
      "start_time": 346958.0,
      "end_time": 349704.0,
      "text": "I will single-handedly end mass incarceration"
    },
    {
      "index": 101,
      "start_time": 349728.0,
      "end_time": 351955.0,
      "text": "and win lots of design awards."
    },
    {
      "index": 102,
      "start_time": 351979.0,
      "end_time": 354752.0,
      "text": "(Laughter)"
    },
    {
      "index": 103,
      "start_time": 354776.0,
      "end_time": 356329.0,
      "text": "And then I checked myself --"
    },
    {
      "index": 104,
      "start_time": 356353.0,
      "end_time": 357815.0,
      "text": "(Laughter)"
    },
    {
      "index": 105,
      "start_time": 357839.0,
      "end_time": 359266.0,
      "text": "because here&#39;s the deal:"
    },
    {
      "index": 106,
      "start_time": 360140.0,
      "end_time": 363523.0,
      "text": "we are incarcerating more of our citizens per capita"
    },
    {
      "index": 107,
      "start_time": 363547.0,
      "end_time": 365156.0,
      "text": "than any country in the world."
    },
    {
      "index": 108,
      "start_time": 365180.0,
      "end_time": 368458.0,
      "text": "And the fastest-growing population there are black women."
    },
    {
      "index": 109,
      "start_time": 368966.0,
      "end_time": 372601.0,
      "text": "Ninety-five percent of all these folks are coming home."
    },
    {
      "index": 110,
      "start_time": 373530.0,
      "end_time": 379931.0,
      "text": "And most of them are survivors of severe sexual, physical and emotional abuse."
    },
    {
      "index": 111,
      "start_time": 380323.0,
      "end_time": 382870.0,
      "text": "They have literally been on both sides of the harm."
    },
    {
      "index": 112,
      "start_time": 383577.0,
      "end_time": 385950.0,
      "text": "So I thought, uh, maybe I should ask them"
    },
    {
      "index": 113,
      "start_time": 385974.0,
      "end_time": 388212.0,
      "text": "what we should build instead of prisons."
    },
    {
      "index": 114,
      "start_time": 389317.0,
      "end_time": 393515.0,
      "text": "So I returned with a restorative justice expert,"
    },
    {
      "index": 115,
      "start_time": 393539.0,
      "end_time": 396643.0,
      "text": "and we started to run the country&#39;s first design studios"
    },
    {
      "index": 116,
      "start_time": 396667.0,
      "end_time": 398537.0,
      "text": "with incarcerated men and women"
    },
    {
      "index": 117,
      "start_time": 398561.0,
      "end_time": 401607.0,
      "text": "around the intersection of restorative justice and design."
    },
    {
      "index": 118,
      "start_time": 402690.0,
      "end_time": 403649.0,
      "text": "And it was transformative for me."
    },
    {
      "index": 119,
      "start_time": 403673.0,
      "end_time": 408800.0,
      "text": "I saw all these people behind walls in a totally different way."
    },
    {
      "index": 120,
      "start_time": 408998.0,
      "end_time": 412784.0,
      "text": "These were souls deeply committed to their personal transformation"
    },
    {
      "index": 121,
      "start_time": 412808.0,
      "end_time": 414274.0,
      "text": "and being accountable."
    },
    {
      "index": 122,
      "start_time": 414602.0,
      "end_time": 417335.0,
      "text": "They were creative, they were visionary."
    },
    {
      "index": 123,
      "start_time": 418490.0,
      "end_time": 420443.0,
      "text": "Danny is one of those souls."
    },
    {
      "index": 124,
      "start_time": 421390.0,
      "end_time": 425871.0,
      "text": "He&#39;s been incarcerated at San Quentin for 27 years"
    },
    {
      "index": 125,
      "start_time": 425895.0,
      "end_time": 428556.0,
      "text": "for taking a life at the age of 21."
    },
    {
      "index": 126,
      "start_time": 429474.0,
      "end_time": 431930.0,
      "text": "From the very beginning,"
    },
    {
      "index": 127,
      "start_time": 431117.0,
      "end_time": 434850.0,
      "text": "he&#39;s been focused on being accountable for that act"
    },
    {
      "index": 128,
      "start_time": 434109.0,
      "end_time": 436959.0,
      "text": "and doing his best to make amends from behind bars."
    },
    {
      "index": 129,
      "start_time": 438458.0,
      "end_time": 444379.0,
      "text": "He brought that work into a design for a community center"
    },
    {
      "index": 130,
      "start_time": 444403.0,
      "end_time": 446536.0,
      "text": "for reconciliation and wellness."
    },
    {
      "index": 131,
      "start_time": 447449.0,
      "end_time": 449125.0,
      "text": "It was a beautiful design, right?"
    },
    {
      "index": 132,
      "start_time": 449149.0,
      "end_time": 452577.0,
      "text": "So it&#39;s this green campus filled with these circular structures"
    },
    {
      "index": 133,
      "start_time": 452601.0,
      "end_time": 454458.0,
      "text": "for victim and offender dialogue."
    },
    {
      "index": 134,
      "start_time": 455149.0,
      "end_time": 457664.0,
      "text": "And when he presented the project to me,"
    },
    {
      "index": 135,
      "start_time": 457688.0,
      "end_time": 459115.0,
      "text": "he started crying."
    },
    {
      "index": 136,
      "start_time": 460133.0,
      "end_time": 465572.0,
      "text": "He said, \"After being in the brutality of San Quentin for so long,"
    },
    {
      "index": 137,
      "start_time": 465596.0,
      "end_time": 468220.0,
      "text": "we don&#39;t think reconciliation will happen."
    },
    {
      "index": 138,
      "start_time": 469611.0,
      "end_time": 473832.0,
      "text": "This design is for a place that fulfills the promise of restorative justice."
    },
    {
      "index": 139,
      "start_time": 475331.0,
      "end_time": 476931.0,
      "text": "And it feels closer now.\""
    },
    {
      "index": 140,
      "start_time": 478720.0,
      "end_time": 481656.0,
      "text": "I know for a fact"
    },
    {
      "index": 141,
      "start_time": 481680.0,
      "end_time": 485950.0,
      "text": "that just the visualization of spaces for restorative justice and healing"
    },
    {
      "index": 142,
      "start_time": 485974.0,
      "end_time": 487133.0,
      "text": "are transformative."
    },
    {
      "index": 143,
      "start_time": 487157.0,
      "end_time": 489680.0,
      "text": "I&#39;ve seen it in our workshops over and over again."
    },
    {
      "index": 144,
      "start_time": 489704.0,
      "end_time": 493458.0,
      "text": "But I think we know that just visualizing these spaces is not enough."
    },
    {
      "index": 145,
      "start_time": 493482.0,
      "end_time": 495153.0,
      "text": "We have to build them."
    },
    {
      "index": 146,
      "start_time": 496188.0,
      "end_time": 499455.0,
      "text": "And so I started to look for justice innovators."
    },
    {
      "index": 147,
      "start_time": 500131.0,
      "end_time": 502270.0,
      "text": "They are not easy to find."
    },
    {
      "index": 148,
      "start_time": 502732.0,
      "end_time": 503938.0,
      "text": "But I found one."
    },
    {
      "index": 149,
      "start_time": 504544.0,
      "end_time": 506847.0,
      "text": "I found the Center for Court Innovation."
    },
    {
      "index": 150,
      "start_time": 507641.0,
      "end_time": 510594.0,
      "text": "They were bringing Native American peacemaking practices"
    },
    {
      "index": 151,
      "start_time": 510618.0,
      "end_time": 512371.0,
      "text": "into a non-Native community"
    },
    {
      "index": 152,
      "start_time": 512395.0,
      "end_time": 514997.0,
      "text": "for the very first time in the United States."
    },
    {
      "index": 153,
      "start_time": 515220.0,
      "end_time": 517610.0,
      "text": "And I approached them, and I said,"
    },
    {
      "index": 154,
      "start_time": 517850.0,
      "end_time": 520450.0,
      "text": "\"OK, well, as you set up your process,"
    },
    {
      "index": 155,
      "start_time": 520679.99999999994,
      "end_time": 523861.99999999994,
      "text": "could I work with the community to design a peacemaking center?\""
    },
    {
      "index": 156,
      "start_time": 525179.0,
      "end_time": 527600.0,
      "text": "And they said yes."
    },
    {
      "index": 157,
      "start_time": 527300.0,
      "end_time": 530363.0,
      "text": "Thank God, because I had no backup to these guys."
    },
    {
      "index": 158,
      "start_time": 531466.0,
      "end_time": 535164.0,
      "text": "And so, in the Near Westside of Syracuse, New York,"
    },
    {
      "index": 159,
      "start_time": 535188.0,
      "end_time": 538879.0,
      "text": "we started to run design workshops with the community"
    },
    {
      "index": 160,
      "start_time": 538903.0,
      "end_time": 542204.0,
      "text": "to both locate and reenvision an old drug house"
    },
    {
      "index": 161,
      "start_time": 542228.0,
      "end_time": 544940.0,
      "text": "to be a peacemaking center."
    },
    {
      "index": 162,
      "start_time": 544537.0,
      "end_time": 547752.0,
      "text": "The Near Westside Peacemaking Project is complete."
    },
    {
      "index": 163,
      "start_time": 547776.0,
      "end_time": 550219.0,
      "text": "And they are already running over 80 circles a year,"
    },
    {
      "index": 164,
      "start_time": 550244.0,
      "end_time": 552425.0,
      "text": "with a very interesting outcome,"
    },
    {
      "index": 165,
      "start_time": 552449.0,
      "end_time": 554117.0,
      "text": "and that it is the space itself"
    },
    {
      "index": 166,
      "start_time": 554142.0,
      "end_time": 556547.0,
      "text": "that&#39;s convincing people to engage in peacemaking"
    },
    {
      "index": 167,
      "start_time": 556571.0,
      "end_time": 558594.0,
      "text": "for the very first time in their lives."
    },
    {
      "index": 168,
      "start_time": 559807.0,
      "end_time": 562918.0,
      "text": "Isabel and her daughter are some of those community members."
    },
    {
      "index": 169,
      "start_time": 562942.0,
      "end_time": 565609.0,
      "text": "And they had been referred to peacemaking"
    },
    {
      "index": 170,
      "start_time": 565633.0,
      "end_time": 569283.0,
      "text": "to heal their relationship after a history of family abuse,"
    },
    {
      "index": 171,
      "start_time": 569307.0,
      "end_time": 570666.0,
      "text": "sexual abuse"
    },
    {
      "index": 172,
      "start_time": 570690.0,
      "end_time": 573516.0,
      "text": "and other issues that they&#39;d been having in their own family"
    },
    {
      "index": 173,
      "start_time": 573540.0,
      "end_time": 574766.0,
      "text": "and the community."
    },
    {
      "index": 174,
      "start_time": 575133.0,
      "end_time": 577760.0,
      "text": "And, you know, Isabel didn&#39;t want to do peacemaking."
    },
    {
      "index": 175,
      "start_time": 577784.0,
      "end_time": 580690.0,
      "text": "She was like, \"This is just like going to court."
    },
    {
      "index": 176,
      "start_time": 580930.0,
      "end_time": 581656.0,
      "text": "What is this peacemaking stuff?\""
    },
    {
      "index": 177,
      "start_time": 581680.0,
      "end_time": 583776.0,
      "text": "But when she showed up,"
    },
    {
      "index": 178,
      "start_time": 583800.0,
      "end_time": 586690.0,
      "text": "she was stressed, she was anxious."
    },
    {
      "index": 179,
      "start_time": 586930.0,
      "end_time": 588680.0,
      "text": "But when she got in, she kind of looked around,"
    },
    {
      "index": 180,
      "start_time": 588705.0,
      "end_time": 590530.0,
      "text": "and she settled in."
    },
    {
      "index": 181,
      "start_time": 590639.0,
      "end_time": 592776.0,
      "text": "And she turned to the coordinator and said,"
    },
    {
      "index": 182,
      "start_time": 593446.0,
      "end_time": 596326.0,
      "text": "\"I feel comfortable here -- at ease."
    },
    {
      "index": 183,
      "start_time": 597410.0,
      "end_time": 598579.0,
      "text": "It&#39;s homey.\""
    },
    {
      "index": 184,
      "start_time": 600720.0,
      "end_time": 602967.0,
      "text": "Isabel and her daughter made a decision that day"
    },
    {
      "index": 185,
      "start_time": 602991.0,
      "end_time": 605783.0,
      "text": "to engage and complete the peacemaking process."
    },
    {
      "index": 186,
      "start_time": 605807.0,
      "end_time": 608815.0,
      "text": "And today, their relationship is transformed;"
    },
    {
      "index": 187,
      "start_time": 608839.0,
      "end_time": 611380.0,
      "text": "they&#39;re doing really well and they&#39;re healing."
    },
    {
      "index": 188,
      "start_time": 612955.0,
      "end_time": 615330.0,
      "text": "So after this project, I didn&#39;t go into a thing"
    },
    {
      "index": 189,
      "start_time": 615354.0,
      "end_time": 617701.0,
      "text": "where I&#39;m going to make a huge peacemaking center."
    },
    {
      "index": 190,
      "start_time": 617725.0,
      "end_time": 622220.0,
      "text": "I did want to have peacemaking centers in every community."
    },
    {
      "index": 191,
      "start_time": 622847.0,
      "end_time": 624826.0,
      "text": "But then a new idea emerged."
    },
    {
      "index": 192,
      "start_time": 625744.0,
      "end_time": 630197.0,
      "text": "I was doing a workshop in Santa Rita Jail in California,"
    },
    {
      "index": 193,
      "start_time": 630221.0,
      "end_time": 633966.0,
      "text": "and one of our incarcerated designers, Doug, said,"
    },
    {
      "index": 194,
      "start_time": 633990.0,
      "end_time": 637411.0,
      "text": "\"Yeah, you know, repairing the harm, getting back on my feet, healing --"
    },
    {
      "index": 195,
      "start_time": 637435.0,
      "end_time": 638751.0,
      "text": "really important."
    },
    {
      "index": 196,
      "start_time": 638775.0,
      "end_time": 641218.0,
      "text": "But the reality is, Deanna, when I get home,"
    },
    {
      "index": 197,
      "start_time": 641243.0,
      "end_time": 643664.0,
      "text": "I don&#39;t have anywhere to go."
    },
    {
      "index": 198,
      "start_time": 643688.0,
      "end_time": 645918.0,
      "text": "I have no job -- who&#39;s going to hire me?"
    },
    {
      "index": 199,
      "start_time": 645942.0,
      "end_time": 647686.0,
      "text": "I&#39;m just going to end up back here.\""
    },
    {
      "index": 200,
      "start_time": 647710.0,
      "end_time": 649410.0,
      "text": "And you know what, he&#39;s right,"
    },
    {
      "index": 201,
      "start_time": 649434.0,
      "end_time": 653656.0,
      "text": "because 60 to 75 percent of those returning to their communities"
    },
    {
      "index": 202,
      "start_time": 653680.0,
      "end_time": 656918.0,
      "text": "will be unemployed a year after their release."
    },
    {
      "index": 203,
      "start_time": 657315.0,
      "end_time": 660942.0,
      "text": "We also know, if you can&#39;t meet your basic economic needs,"
    },
    {
      "index": 204,
      "start_time": 660966.0,
      "end_time": 662463.0,
      "text": "you&#39;re going to commit crime --"
    },
    {
      "index": 205,
      "start_time": 662487.0,
      "end_time": 663843.0,
      "text": "any of us would do that."
    },
    {
      "index": 206,
      "start_time": 665173.0,
      "end_time": 668839.0,
      "text": "So instead of building prisons,"
    },
    {
      "index": 207,
      "start_time": 668863.0,
      "end_time": 673474.0,
      "text": "what we could build are spaces for job training and entrepreneurship."
    },
    {
      "index": 208,
      "start_time": 673498.0,
      "end_time": 676655.0,
      "text": "These are spaces for what we call \"restorative economics.\""
    },
    {
      "index": 209,
      "start_time": 677387.0,
      "end_time": 680252.0,
      "text": "Located in East Oakland, California,"
    },
    {
      "index": 210,
      "start_time": 680276.0,
      "end_time": 683450.0,
      "text": "\"Restore Oakland\" will be the country’s first center"
    },
    {
      "index": 211,
      "start_time": 683700.0,
      "end_time": 685664.0,
      "text": "for restorative justice and restorative economics."
    },
    {
      "index": 212,
      "start_time": 685688.0,
      "end_time": 691728.0,
      "text": "(Applause)"
    },
    {
      "index": 213,
      "start_time": 691752.0,
      "end_time": 693354.0,
      "text": "So here&#39;s what we&#39;re going to do."
    },
    {
      "index": 214,
      "start_time": 693379.0,
      "end_time": 696585.0,
      "text": "We&#39;re going to gut this building and turn it into three things."
    },
    {
      "index": 215,
      "start_time": 696609.0,
      "end_time": 698887.0,
      "text": "First, a restaurant called \"Colors,\""
    },
    {
      "index": 216,
      "start_time": 698911.0,
      "end_time": 701760.0,
      "text": "that will break the racial divide in the restaurant industry"
    },
    {
      "index": 217,
      "start_time": 701784.0,
      "end_time": 703784.0,
      "text": "by training low-wage restaurant workers"
    },
    {
      "index": 218,
      "start_time": 703808.0,
      "end_time": 705752.0,
      "text": "to get living-wage jobs in fine dining."
    },
    {
      "index": 219,
      "start_time": 705776.0,
      "end_time": 708449.0,
      "text": "It does not matter if you have a criminal record or not."
    },
    {
      "index": 220,
      "start_time": 708839.0,
      "end_time": 712514.0,
      "text": "On the second floor, we have bright, open, airy spaces"
    },
    {
      "index": 221,
      "start_time": 712538.0,
      "end_time": 715705.0,
      "text": "to support a constellation of activist organizations"
    },
    {
      "index": 222,
      "start_time": 715729.0,
      "end_time": 719164.0,
      "text": "to amplify their cry of \"Healthcare Not Handcuffs,\""
    },
    {
      "index": 223,
      "start_time": 719188.0,
      "end_time": 720778.0,
      "text": "and \"Housing as a human right.\""
    },
    {
      "index": 224,
      "start_time": 721276.0,
      "end_time": 726767.0,
      "text": "And third, the county&#39;s first dedicated space for restorative justice,"
    },
    {
      "index": 225,
      "start_time": 726792.0,
      "end_time": 730379.0,
      "text": "filled with nature, color, texture and spaces of refuge"
    },
    {
      "index": 226,
      "start_time": 730403.0,
      "end_time": 732331.0,
      "text": "to support the dialogues here."
    },
    {
      "index": 227,
      "start_time": 732804.0,
      "end_time": 735438.0,
      "text": "This project breaks ground in just two months."
    },
    {
      "index": 228,
      "start_time": 735820.0,
      "end_time": 737422.0,
      "text": "And we have plans to replicate it"
    },
    {
      "index": 229,
      "start_time": 737446.0,
      "end_time": 740962.0,
      "text": "in Washington D.C., Detroit, New York and New Orleans."
    },
    {
      "index": 230,
      "start_time": 740986.0,
      "end_time": 746424.0,
      "text": "(Applause)"
    },
    {
      "index": 231,
      "start_time": 750609.0,
      "end_time": 753680.0,
      "text": "So you&#39;ve seen two things we can build instead of prisons."
    },
    {
      "index": 232,
      "start_time": 753704.0,
      "end_time": 756228.0,
      "text": "And look, the price point is better."
    },
    {
      "index": 233,
      "start_time": 756252.0,
      "end_time": 760852.0,
      "text": "For one jail, we can build 30 restorative justice centers."
    },
    {
      "index": 234,
      "start_time": 760876.0,
      "end_time": 762356.0,
      "text": "(Applause)"
    },
    {
      "index": 235,
      "start_time": 762380.0,
      "end_time": 764966.0,
      "text": "That is a better use of your tax dollars."
    },
    {
      "index": 236,
      "start_time": 765982.0,
      "end_time": 768115.0,
      "text": "So I want to build all of these."
    },
    {
      "index": 237,
      "start_time": 768712.0,
      "end_time": 771131.0,
      "text": "But building buildings is a really heavy lift."
    },
    {
      "index": 238,
      "start_time": 771155.0,
      "end_time": 772305.0,
      "text": "It takes time."
    },
    {
      "index": 239,
      "start_time": 773188.0,
      "end_time": 776610.0,
      "text": "And what was happening in the communities that I was serving"
    },
    {
      "index": 240,
      "start_time": 776850.0,
      "end_time": 780818.0,
      "text": "is we were losing people every week to gun violence and mass incarceration."
    },
    {
      "index": 241,
      "start_time": 781521.0,
      "end_time": 785723.0,
      "text": "We needed to serve more people and faster and keep them out of the system."
    },
    {
      "index": 242,
      "start_time": 786720.0,
      "end_time": 789307.0,
      "text": "And a new idea emerged from the community,"
    },
    {
      "index": 243,
      "start_time": 789331.0,
      "end_time": 791931.0,
      "text": "one that was a lot lighter on its feet."
    },
    {
      "index": 244,
      "start_time": 792918.0,
      "end_time": 796843.0,
      "text": "Instead of building prisons, we could build villages on wheels."
    },
    {
      "index": 245,
      "start_time": 798640.0,
      "end_time": 801218.0,
      "text": "It&#39;s called the Pop-Up Resource Village,"
    },
    {
      "index": 246,
      "start_time": 801243.0,
      "end_time": 804116.0,
      "text": "and it brings an entire constellation of resources"
    },
    {
      "index": 247,
      "start_time": 804140.0,
      "end_time": 807347.0,
      "text": "to isolated communities in the greater San Francisco area,"
    },
    {
      "index": 248,
      "start_time": 807371.0,
      "end_time": 810966.0,
      "text": "including mobile medical, social services and pop-up shops."
    },
    {
      "index": 249,
      "start_time": 812220.0,
      "end_time": 813378.0,
      "text": "And so what we&#39;re doing now"
    },
    {
      "index": 250,
      "start_time": 813402.0,
      "end_time": 816164.0,
      "text": "is we&#39;re building this whole village with the community,"
    },
    {
      "index": 251,
      "start_time": 816188.0,
      "end_time": 821530.0,
      "text": "starting with transforming municipal buses into classrooms on wheels"
    },
    {
      "index": 252,
      "start_time": 821770.0,
      "end_time": 824982.0,
      "text": "that bring GED and high school education across turf lines."
    },
    {
      "index": 253,
      "start_time": 825600.0,
      "end_time": 826156.0,
      "text": "(Applause)"
    },
    {
      "index": 254,
      "start_time": 826181.0,
      "end_time": 829740.0,
      "text": "We will serve thousands of more students with this."
    },
    {
      "index": 255,
      "start_time": 829581.0,
      "end_time": 831792.0,
      "text": "We&#39;re creating mobile spaces of refuge"
    },
    {
      "index": 256,
      "start_time": 831816.0,
      "end_time": 834459.0,
      "text": "for women released from jail in the middle of the night,"
    },
    {
      "index": 257,
      "start_time": 834483.0,
      "end_time": 835800.0,
      "text": "at their most vulnerable."
    },
    {
      "index": 258,
      "start_time": 836246.0,
      "end_time": 840109.0,
      "text": "Next summer, the village will launch, and it pops up every single week,"
    },
    {
      "index": 259,
      "start_time": 840133.0,
      "end_time": 843344.0,
      "text": "expanding to more and more communities as it goes."
    },
    {
      "index": 260,
      "start_time": 844770.0,
      "end_time": 845355.0,
      "text": "So look out for it."
    },
    {
      "index": 261,
      "start_time": 845379.0,
      "end_time": 850387.0,
      "text": "(Applause)"
    },
    {
      "index": 262,
      "start_time": 850411.0,
      "end_time": 853176.0,
      "text": "So what do we build instead of prisons?"
    },
    {
      "index": 263,
      "start_time": 853807.0,
      "end_time": 855339.0,
      "text": "We&#39;ve looked at three things:"
    },
    {
      "index": 264,
      "start_time": 855363.0,
      "end_time": 856783.0,
      "text": "peacemaking centers,"
    },
    {
      "index": 265,
      "start_time": 856807.0,
      "end_time": 860212.0,
      "text": "centers for restorative justice and restorative economics"
    },
    {
      "index": 266,
      "start_time": 860236.0,
      "end_time": 861569.0,
      "text": "and pop-up villages."
    },
    {
      "index": 267,
      "start_time": 863380.0,
      "end_time": 866434.0,
      "text": "But I&#39;m telling you, I have a list a mile long."
    },
    {
      "index": 268,
      "start_time": 867403.0,
      "end_time": 870990.0,
      "text": "This is customized housing for youth transitioning out of foster care."
    },
    {
      "index": 269,
      "start_time": 871140.0,
      "end_time": 874291.0,
      "text": "These are reentry centers for women to reunite with their children."
    },
    {
      "index": 270,
      "start_time": 874315.0,
      "end_time": 877249.0,
      "text": "These are spaces for survivors of violence."
    },
    {
      "index": 271,
      "start_time": 877807.0,
      "end_time": 880934.0,
      "text": "These are spaces that address the root causes"
    },
    {
      "index": 272,
      "start_time": 880958.0,
      "end_time": 882569.0,
      "text": "of mass incarceration."
    },
    {
      "index": 273,
      "start_time": 882593.0,
      "end_time": 886497.0,
      "text": "And not a single one of them is a jail or a prison."
    },
    {
      "index": 274,
      "start_time": 888300.0,
      "end_time": 892521.0,
      "text": "Activist, philosopher, writer Cornel West says"
    },
    {
      "index": 275,
      "start_time": 893363.0,
      "end_time": 895934.0,
      "text": "that \"Justice is what love looks like in public.\""
    },
    {
      "index": 276,
      "start_time": 896871.0,
      "end_time": 901290.0,
      "text": "So with this in mind, I ask you one more time"
    },
    {
      "index": 277,
      "start_time": 901315.0,
      "end_time": 904130.0,
      "text": "to imagine a world without prisons,"
    },
    {
      "index": 278,
      "start_time": 905380.0,
      "end_time": 908712.0,
      "text": "and join me in creating all the things that we could build instead."
    },
    {
      "index": 279,
      "start_time": 909545.0,
      "end_time": 910695.0,
      "text": "Thank you."
    },
    {
      "index": 280,
      "start_time": 910720.0,
      "end_time": 917613.0,
      "text": "(Applause)"
    }
  ]
}